dct_description_sm: "Contour interval 10 metre". Relief is not shown as indicated on legend. Shows roads, railways, important places and buildings, and density of built-up areas. "Government of Pākistān copyright reserved." Area surveyed 1995-96. "REG. No. 89 RWD '97 ..." "List of names and other miscellaneous information is printed on reverse. On verso: Sketch map of Mīrpur.
